                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.015315/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jones</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-01-16T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 16, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram December 9, 4 p.m. and despatch No. 72 of December 16.</p>
                <p>Should you not have received satisfactory reply to your note of December 11 to
                    Minister for Foreign Affairs, you will request immediate suitable amends from
                    Honduran Government for insult to flag.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
